OL,3,CBottled water stations set up as
OL,4,Cthousands left without supply
OL,6,FBottled water stations have been set
OL,7,Fup at locations across Flintshire as
OL,8,Fthousands of households are cut-off
OL,9,Ffrom their water supply.
OL,11,FDwr Cymru Welsh Water said it is
OL,12,Fworking to repair a burst mains pipe,
OL,13,Fafter an initial attempt to fix it
OL,14,Ffailed.
OL,16,FCommunities affected include: Flint,
OL,17,FHolywell, Ffynnongroyw, Greenfield,
OL,18,FLlanerch y Mor, Mostyn, Oakenholt,
OL,19,FTalacre, Whitford, Queensferry,
OL,20,FShotton, Connah's Quay, Garden City,
OL,21,FHawarden, Mancot and Sandycroft.
