OL,3,CBottled water stations set up as
OL,4,Cthousands left without supply
OL,6,FChief Executive of Dwr Cymru Welsh
OL,7,FWater, Peter Perry, apologised to all
OL,8,Faffected customers. He explained:
OL,9,F"We've got a burst on a strategic
OL,10,Ftrunk main that's been incredibly
OL,11,Fdifficult to repair, first of all in
OL,12,Fterms of safety of our workforce and
OL,13,Fsecondly in terms of very, very
OL,14,Fdifficult ground conditions.
OL,16,F"We repaired the mains once last
OL,17,Fweekend and unfortunately that repair
OL,18,Fdidn't hold.
