OL,3,CBottled water stations set up as
OL,4,Cthousands left without supply
OL,6,F"We didn't want to shut the main off
OL,7,Fwith a heatwave coming through so we
OL,8,Ftried to keep as many customers in
OL,9,Fsupply so that we could carry out a
OL,10,Ffull repair later this week.
OL,11,FUnfortunately the initial repair has
OL,12,Fnow failed and that means that
OL,13,Fsupplies are now off to a large number
OL,14,Fof customers in north east Wales and I
OL,15,Fam very, very sorry for that."
OL,17,FHe added: "We're doing all we can,
OL,18,Fwe're working around the clock to get
OL,19,Fthe repair done and we're hopeful of
OL,20,Fgetting that done later today (14
OL,21,FAugust)."
